    customers_data

    customers_data.Rd

    Generate N samples of random customer data

    customers_data(.N_customers)

    Arguments

    .N_customers

    Number of random observations to generate

    Value

    A dataframe with .N_customers observations and 7 variables

    Examples

    customers_data(.N_customers=1000)
